{"id": "7790", "post": "<div class=\"post-7790 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-bitcoins tag-budapest tag-exclusive tag-hungary tag-ipv6 tag-mikrovps-eu tag-openvz tag-storage\" id=\"post-7790\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/mikrovps-openvz-and-storage-vps-in-budapest-hungary-starting-at-5-67-quarterly/\" rel=\"bookmark\">MikroVPS \u2013 OpenVZ and Storage VPS in Budapest, Hungary starting at $5.67 / Quarterly</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/bitcoins/\" rel=\"tag\">bitcoins</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/budapest/\" rel=\"tag\">Budapest</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/exclusive/\" rel=\"tag\">exclusive</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/hungary/\" rel=\"tag\">Hungary</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ipv6/\" rel=\"tag\">ipv6</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/mikrovps-eu/\" rel=\"tag\">mikrovps.eu</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\" rel=\"tag\">openvz</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/storage/\" rel=\"tag\">storage</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> October 10, 2015 @ 1:00 am, by Jonathan Tan</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://www.mikrovps.eu/\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTg4IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE4OCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot alignnone size-medium wp-image-5615\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/MikroVPS_Cost-effective_IT_solutions_-_2014-08-11_15.24.22-300x188.png.webp\" alt=\"MikroVPS_Cost-effective_IT_solutions_-_2014-08-11_15.24.22\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/MikroVPS_Cost-effective_IT_solutions_-_2014-08-11_15.24.22-300x188.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/MikroVPS_Cost-effective_IT_solutions_-_2014-08-11_15.24.22-1024x642.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/MikroVPS_Cost-effective_IT_solutions_-_2014-08-11_15.24.22.png.webp 1263w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"></a></p><p>Janos, from <a href=\"https://www.mikrovps.eu/\">MikroVPS</a>, is back with an exclusive offer for the LowEndBox readers that gives 50% recurring, life-time discount with the promo code <strong>LEB50VPS</strong>. This is applicable to their regular OpenVZ plans and one of their new product type: high storage VPS. The storage plans are ideal for backup server, or file server for sharing huge files, and also great for torrent server.</p><p>Our readers will be glad to know also that IPv6 (/112 pool are available for request)) is supported and virtual currency payments via bitcoins are accepted. Servers are available in Budapest, Hungary.</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>VZ-256M</strong><p></p><ul><li>256MB RAM</li><li>1 CPU cores</li><li>CPU units: 2,000</li><li>10GB HDD space</li><li>100GB transfer</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>native IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB50VPS</strong></li><li>$5.67 / Quarterly</li><li><a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/cart.php?a=add&amp;language=English&amp;currency=3&amp;promocode=LEB50VPS&amp;billingcycle=quarterly&amp;pid=174\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>VZ-512M</strong><p></p><ul><li>512MB RAM</li><li>2 CPU cores</li><li>CPU units: 5,000</li><li>25GB HDD space</li><li>250GB transfer</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>native IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB50VPS</strong></li><li>$6.50 / Quarterly</li><li><a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/cart.php?a=add&amp;language=English&amp;currency=3&amp;promocode=LEB50VPS&amp;billingcycle=quarterly&amp;pid=175\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>VZ-1G</strong><p></p><ul><li>1024MB RAM</li><li>2 CPU cores</li><li>CPU units: 10,000</li><li>50GB HDD space</li><li>500GB transfer</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>native IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB50VPS</strong></li><li>$8.54 / Quarterly</li><li><a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/cart.php?a=add&amp;language=English&amp;currency=3&amp;promocode=LEB50VPS&amp;billingcycle=quarterly&amp;pid=176\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>VZ-2G</strong><p></p><ul><li>2048MB RAM</li><li>3 CPU cores</li><li>CPU units: 20,000</li><li>100GB HDD space</li><li>1024GB transfer</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>native IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB50VPS</strong></li><li>$12.25 / Quarterly</li><li><a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/cart.php?a=add&amp;language=English&amp;currency=3&amp;promocode=LEB50VPS&amp;billingcycle=quarterly&amp;pid=177\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><em>Listed prices already include the discount. Note that more OpenVZ VPS are available in their <a href=\"http://www.mikrovps.com/vps/openvz\">website</a>. More offers inside!</em></p><p>MikroVPS Ltd. started their business back in April of 2012, with EU VAT HU25189861. They have been featured in LowEndBox <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/mikrovps-eu/\">multiple times</a> before and their offers have generated lots of interest. There are two kinds of nodes for OpenVZ VPS. Their AMD based servers have SuperMicro 813MTQ-350CB 1U chassis, SuperMicro H8SCM-F motherboard, AMD Opteron 4280 CPU (8 core @ 2.8 GHz), 32GB RAM, HP P410 RAID controller with BBU, Hot-swap 4x 1TB WD Black SATA HDD in RAID10, and 1 GBit/s connection. Their Intel based nodes have HP DL160 G6, 2x Intel Xeon E5540 CPU, 32GB RAM, HP P410 RAID controller with BBU, Hot-swap 4x 1TB HP SATA HDD in RAID10, and 1 GBit/s connection.</p><p><span id=\"more-7790\"></span></p><p>There are two plans for their high storage VPS:</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>BU-200</strong><p></p><ul><li>256MB RAM</li><li>1 CPU cores</li><li>CPU units: 10,000</li><li>200GB HDD space</li><li>900GB transfer</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>native IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB50VPS</strong></li><li>$11.13 / Quarterly</li><li><a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/cart.php?a=add&amp;language=English&amp;currency=3&amp;promocode=LEB50VPS&amp;billingcycle=quarterly&amp;pid=407\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>BU-400</strong><p></p><ul><li>512MB RAM</li><li>1 CPU cores</li><li>CPU units: 20,000</li><li>400GB HDD space</li><li>1800GB transfer</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>native IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/SolusVM</li><li>Coupon: <strong>LEB50VPS</strong></li><li>$19.10 / Quarterly</li><li><a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/cart.php?a=add&amp;language=English&amp;currency=3&amp;promocode=LEB50VPS&amp;billingcycle=quarterly&amp;pid=408\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Accepted payment methods are credit card, PayPal, Transferwise (bank transfer) and BitCoin. Outgoing SMTP is filtered for all plans by detault. Note that they have 99.9% SLA. As always, kindly read their <a href=\"https://my.mikrovps.hu/downloads/3/GTC\">Terms of Service</a> before making a purchase.</p><p><strong>Network information</strong></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Doclerweb DC \u2013 Budapest, Hungary (DMCA free)</span><br>\nTest IPv4: 185.112.156.3<br>\nTest IPv6: 2a02:6080::1:10<br>\nTest file (100M): <a href=\"http://test.mikrovps.hu/100M.test\">http://test.mikrovps.hu/100M.test</a><br>\nTest file (1GB): <a href=\"http://test.mikrovps.hu/1G.test\">http://test.mikrovps.hu/1G.test</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shap